      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "吓，小姐来了么呀，啐。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902156_e00004",
      "play_id": "70902156",
      "scene_id": "70902156_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "临镜序",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "原来是风弄竹声，只道是金珮响，月移花影疑是玉人来。意孜孜双业眼，急攘攘那情怀，倚定门儿待。只索要呆打孩，青鸾黄犬信音乖。",
      "text_length": 60
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902156_e00005",
      "play_id": "70902156",
      "scene_id": "70902156_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张珙下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
